      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AKINA ROCKY (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (23.23) in a Grade 4/5 at Warragul. Should bounce back. PAW QUANDA (4) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 2.25 lengths at Shepparton in a handy 22.21 beating More Rage. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. One of the prime contenders. ZIPPING TYRA (2) is having her first start around this circuit. Last start placegetter (23.64) at Horsham off this same draw. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from four attempts. Expected to be in this for a long way. ROYAL PRIDE (6) is a last start winner who can measure up again.",
